-- Hong Kong Property Curbs Aimed at Short-Term Speculation, SHK's Lui Says
-- B y   K e l v i n   W o n g
-- 2010-12-02T04:49:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-02/hong-kong-property-curbs-aimed-at-short-term-speculation-shk-s-lui-says.html
Hong Kong’s property curbs are aimed
at curbing short-term speculation and will be good for the
market in the long term, Victor Lui, Sun Hung Kai Properties
Ltd. executive director of the company’s property arm, said at a
shareholder meeting today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
